high_descs: Cross the room to stand in front of the dresser with the laptop on it.
Pick up the green bowl next to the laptop from the dresser.
Turn left and then move to stand between the coffee table and the wall.
Set the bowl on the coffee table past the remote control and to the right of the book.
Turn and return to the long dresser where you originally got the green bowl.
Pick up the yellow container that's to the left of the laptop.
Turn left and carry the yellow container to the coffee table so you're standing between the table and the wall.
Place the yellow container to the right of the green bowl.
anns.task_desc: Move two containers from the dresser to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the table with the green bowl.
Pick up the green bowl from the table.
Turn left, then left again to face the center table with the lap-top.
Put the green bowl on the center table.
Turn left, then right, then left to face the table with the statue.
Pick up the golden container from the table.
Turn left, then right, then left to face the center table.
Put the golden container on top of the center table.
anns.task_desc: Move two items from a counter table to a center table.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk over to a dresser.
Pick up a green bowl from the dresser.
Turn left, then left again and walk towards a coffee table.
Place the bowl on the coffee table.
Turn to your left, then walk back over to the dresser.
Pick up a gold pot from the dresser.
Turn left and walk back over to the coffee table.
Place the pot on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl and a pot onto a coffee table.
